  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.t2A5PzInAqmErLzK]{Goo Grenade (Lesser)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.wi97vRj8IXx3wLmZ]{Goo Grenade (Moderate)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.SAtG9jrqey2y8EGb]{Goo Grenade (Greater)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.W0RWd2E0jkF2ZXhf]{Goo Grenade (Major)}</p>\n<p>When you hit a creature with a goo grenade, that creature takes persistent acid damage and a circumstance penalty to its Speeds from the clinging goo.</p>\n<p>The target can end any penalties, conditions, and persistent damage caused by the bomb by Escaping or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to pry themselves free of the ooze. These Interact actions don't have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.</p>"
